  "detailed_description": "Dungeons of Necromancers is a small pixel game.<br>Your task is to go through as many dungeons as possible while upgrading your character.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967370/extras/6148f73e502ef51052462f43873bea37.poster.avif?t=1711405078\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967370/extras/6148f73e502ef51052462f43873bea37.webm?t=1711405078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967370/extras/6148f73e502ef51052462f43873bea37.mp4?t=1711405078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The path to the dungeons of necromancers is open.<br>You have to fight with many necromancers and their creations.<br><br>Defeat all enemies in the dungeon to open a portal to the next dungeon.<br>With each dungeon, enemies get stronger, fiercer and bigger.<br><br>All walls in the dungeons are completely destructible. Destroy dungeons to reach opponents or find treasures.<br>You can not only destroy but also build walls. Use this ability in combat.<br>Put walls in front of the enemy to get a tactical advantage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967370/extras/55af46b20fdc9906a6c1aff147a60114.poster.avif?t=1711405078\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967370/extras/55af46b20fdc9906a6c1aff147a60114.webm?t=1711405078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967370/extras/55af46b20fdc9906a6c1aff147a60114.mp4?t=1711405078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>On the way of your journey there will be potions that increase the parameters of your character.<br>Potions can be bought in the store, which is in each dungeon, but they need to be found.<br><br>Also, your character has a permanent progression. Before the new descent into the dungeon you will get to the character upgrade menu.<br>Unlike potions, upgrades remains forever, even after the death of your character.<br><br>How deep can you descent to the dungeons?",
  "about_the_game": "Dungeons of Necromancers is a small pixel game.<br>Your task is to go through as many dungeons as possible while upgrading your character.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967370/extras/6148f73e502ef51052462f43873bea37.poster.avif?t=1711405078\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967370/extras/6148f73e502ef51052462f43873bea37.webm?t=1711405078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967370/extras/6148f73e502ef51052462f43873bea37.mp4?t=1711405078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The path to the dungeons of necromancers is open.<br>You have to fight with many necromancers and their creations.<br><br>Defeat all enemies in the dungeon to open a portal to the next dungeon.<br>With each dungeon, enemies get stronger, fiercer and bigger.<br><br>All walls in the dungeons are completely destructible. Destroy dungeons to reach opponents or find treasures.<br>You can not only destroy but also build walls. Use this ability in combat.<br>Put walls in front of the enemy to get a tactical advantage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967370/extras/55af46b20fdc9906a6c1aff147a60114.poster.avif?t=1711405078\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967370/extras/55af46b20fdc9906a6c1aff147a60114.webm?t=1711405078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967370/extras/55af46b20fdc9906a6c1aff147a60114.mp4?t=1711405078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>On the way of your journey there will be potions that increase the parameters of your character.<br>Potions can be bought in the store, which is in each dungeon, but they need to be found.<br><br>Also, your character has a permanent progression. Before the new descent into the dungeon you will get to the character upgrade menu.<br>Unlike potions, upgrades remains forever, even after the death of your character.<br><br>How deep can you descent to the dungeons?",
